name: The Last Power
description: So much going on around this simulation. I don't have anything left, thus the power that doesn't belong to me either. Encircled our kaleidoscope emotion got me thinking, do I need to live any longer just to see humanity suffered? Guess no one knows what's the 'real' answer is. // 1500px x 1500px 72 DPI (2.075.193 bytes)
